	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Heals about 1/6 of an 8th level pet.  Main problem with the spell is its slow recovery time.  It is highly effective when used in combination with dark empathy however.  Empathy has a faster recovery time and you can shoot off your next mend bones when you recover from the empathy.  The combination of the 2 spells with almost double the effectiveness of you pet.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#D6D1BE">
		
	
