		</td>
	
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This spell is best used when fighting poison creatures, or disease ones at low level.  Cast a heat blood or poison spell to attract the attention of your new foe, tell your pet to attack.  Then keep your pet buff while he kills the foe.  Remember the new F1 twice command to target your pet; this way you can stand so that the target is easily targeted again.  If the target runs, cast a quick life sucking spell and over it keels.  At higher levels, this spell can be kicked off very quickly.  Also, high level pets take a long time to heal and this spell makes it much more bearable to wait the med time.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
