			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			For some reason if I cast this spell while my pet is in combat, it does'nt seem to do anything at all.   Nada.   However, it heals him considerably if cast outside combat.  As some of my pets occaisonally heal very slowly, this is good for speeding up the rate you can handle fights if you're not expending mana at too fast a rate.
			</font>
	
