		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			I didnt get this spell at first, due to the advice of other players.  I find that after using it in battle i completely disagree with those other players.  It helps me to keep my pet alive during battle so i dont have to enter melee personally.  It is mana efficient too - as far as i can see, and quick casting.  I use it after casting poison bolt &amp; clinging darkness, then i check on my pet health.  if down to around half, I cast mend bones &amp; then go back to my monster. this works great in conjunction w/ dark pact!  Try it, it works.
			</font>
	
