			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Mend bones is an awesome spell. its casting time is less than dark empathy, but costs 5 more mana. Also, if it doesn't seem to have an effect, that's because your pet just got wacked hard, and it's countering the normal decrease of his hp bar. It's mana efficient, looks cool,and heals the equiv of 30 hp. The bone walk spell usually gives you a pet at 200 hp. when you cast this, it heals him about 15% of his total hp, which is 30 hp.
			</font>
	
